{
  "page": "Tourney for King Viserys I's accession",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>tourney for King Viserys I's accession</b> was held at <a href=\"/index.php/Maidenpool\" title=\"Maidenpool\">Maidenpool</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/104_AC\" title=\"104 AC\">104&#160;AC</a>. It honored King <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys I Targaryen\">Viserys I Targaryen</a>, who had recently succeeded King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#The_Melee\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">The Melee</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#The_Joust\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">The Joust</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_for_King_Viserys_I%27s_accession&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The twenty-two-year-old Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Criston_Cole\" title=\"Criston Cole\">Criston Cole</a> defeated Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Targaryen\" title=\"Daemon Targaryen\">Daemon Targaryen</a>, the brother of Viserys, in the <a href=\"/index.php/Melee\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Melee\">melee</a> by knocking aside <a href=\"/index.php/Dark_Sister\" title=\"Dark Sister\">Dark Sister</a> with his <a href=\"/index.php/Armament\" title=\"Armament\">morningstar</a>. He then gave the <a href=\"/index.php/Queen_of_love_and_beauty\" title=\"Queen of love and beauty\">victor's laurel</a> to the seven-year-old Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a> and asked to wear her favor in the lists. Criston subsequently became a favorite at court and joined the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a> the following year taking the slot left vacant by the death of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ryam_Redwyne\" title=\"Ryam Redwyne\">Ryam Redwyne</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Melee\">The Melee</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_for_King_Viserys_I%27s_accession&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Melee\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Cole\" title=\"House Cole\"><img alt=\"House Cole.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/be/House_Cole.svg/32px-House_Cole.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/be/House_Cole.svg/48px-House_Cole.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/be/House_Cole.svg/64px-House_Cole.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/32px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/48px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/64px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Criston_Cole\" title=\"Criston Cole\">Criston Cole</a> won the melee, his final opponent being Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Targaryen\" title=\"Daemon Targaryen\">Daemon Targaryen</a>.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Joust\">The Joust</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_for_King_Viserys_I%27s_accession&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Joust\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Cole\" title=\"House Cole\"><img alt=\"House Cole.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/be/House_Cole.svg/32px-House_Cole.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/be/House_Cole.svg/48px-House_Cole.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/be/House_Cole.svg/64px-House_Cole.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/32px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/48px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/64px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Criston_Cole\" title=\"Criston Cole\">Criston Cole</a> defeated Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Targaryen\" title=\"Daemon Targaryen\">Daemon Targaryen</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Cole\" title=\"House Cole\"><img alt=\"House Cole.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/be/House_Cole.svg/32px-House_Cole.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/be/House_Cole.svg/48px-House_Cole.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/be/House_Cole.svg/64px-House_Cole.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Cargyll\" title=\"House Cargyll\"><img alt=\"House Cargyll.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/4c/House_Cargyll.svg/32px-House_Cargyll.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/4c/House_Cargyll.svg/48px-House_Cargyll.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/4c/House_Cargyll.svg/64px-House_Cargyll.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Criston_Cole\" title=\"Criston Cole\">Criston Cole</a> defeated Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Arryk_Cargyll\" title=\"Arryk Cargyll\">Arryk Cargyll</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Cole\" title=\"House Cole\"><img alt=\"House Cole.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/be/House_Cole.svg/32px-House_Cole.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/be/House_Cole.svg/48px-House_Cole.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/be/House_Cole.svg/64px-House_Cole.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Cargyll\" title=\"House Cargyll\"><img alt=\"House Cargyll.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/4c/House_Cargyll.svg/32px-House_Cargyll.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/4c/House_Cargyll.svg/48px-House_Cargyll.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/4c/House_Cargyll.svg/64px-House_Cargyll.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Criston_Cole\" title=\"Criston Cole\">Criston Cole</a> defeated Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Erryk_Cargyll\" title=\"Erryk Cargyll\">Erryk Cargyll</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Mallister\" title=\"House Mallister\"><img alt=\"House Mallister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/75/House_Mallister.svg/32px-House_Mallister.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/75/House_Mallister.svg/48px-House_Mallister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/75/House_Mallister.svg/64px-House_Mallister.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Cole\" title=\"House Cole\"><img alt=\"House Cole.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/be/House_Cole.svg/32px-House_Cole.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/be/House_Cole.svg/48px-House_Cole.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/be/House_Cole.svg/64px-House_Cole.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lymond_Mallister\" title=\"Lymond Mallister\">Lymond Mallister</a> defeated Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Criston_Cole\" title=\"Criston Cole\">Criston Cole</a>.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_for_King_Viserys_I%27s_accession&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Heirs of the Dragon - A Question of Succession.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403115142\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.067 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.360 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 329/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8918/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1902/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 478/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpe